{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This demo is a peek at Ad Memoriam - an in-development mystery game about a band with a curse: at every single one of their concerts, someone dies in an accident. When Erica - Ad Memoriam superfan, amateur detective, and Alicia\u2019s best friend - becomes the next victim, Alicia realizes that the deaths may not be as accidental as they seem. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play the first chapter of Alicia's journey as she unravels the strange circumstances around her own best friend's death, and takes her first step into the mystery of Ad Memoriam.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>EXPLORE THE SCENE</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241390/extras/9.png?t=1728915084\" />Walk through each concert venue and get a lay of the land before and after a victim dies. Search for clues, spot any inconsistencies, and find evidence to back up your theories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>NOBODY KNOWS THE TRUTH</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241390/extras/20241014202359_1.jpg?t=1728915084\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interview other concertgoers and venue staff about what they've seen. In a setting as hectic and crowded as a concert, there's bound to be lots of witnesses - but can any of them be trusted to give an accurate testimony? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>RECONSTRUCT THE INCIDENT</strong> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241390/extras/20241014200826_1.jpg?t=1728915084\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use witness accounts to identify the sequence of events that lead up to each accident. Piece together the truth from half-remembered details, conflicting testimonies, and lies. Put the chaos of the incident in ord